Package com.sympos2.models

Class Usuario

java.lang.Object
com.sympos2.models.Usuario
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, org.springframework.security.core.userdetails.UserDetails
public class Usuario extends Object implements org.springframework.security.core.userdetails.UserDetails
This is the class to creates Usuario objects, which represents student, titled and admin users in database by the parameter: "role".

0.1.0

  • Constructor Details

    • Usuario

      public Usuario()

    • Usuario

      public Usuario(String id, String name, LocalDate fechaNac, String email, String password, String avatar, String role, String studies, String school)
      Constructor for creating a "Student" user with the specified attributes. This constructor initializes an instance of the Usuario class with the provided values for user details, including the user's ID, name, birth date, email, password, avatar, studies, and school.
      Parameters:
      id - String which collects the ObjectId of the user.
      name - String with the user's name.
      fechaNac - LocalDate with the user's birthday.
      email - String with the user's email address.
      password - String with the user's password.
      avatar - String with the avatar image URL of the user.
      studies - String with the studies the user is currently pursuing.
      school - String with the institution where the user is studying.

    • Usuario

      public Usuario(String id, String name, LocalDate fechaNac, String email, String password, String avatar, String role, Long phone)
      Constructor for creating an "Administrator" user with the specified attributes. This constructor initializes an instance of the Usuario class with the provided values for user details, including the user's ID, name, birth date, email, password, avatar, and phone number. Additionally, the user's role is set to "ADMIN".
      Parameters:
      id - String which collects the ObjectId of the user.
      name - String with the user's name.
      fechaNac - LocalDate with the user's birthday.
      email - String with the user's email address.
      password - String with the user's password.
      avatar - String with the avatar image URL of the user.
      phone - Long with the user's phone number.

    • Usuario

      public Usuario(String id, String name, LocalDate fechaNac, String email, String password, String avatar, String role, String studies_title, String study_place, LocalDate title_date, String title_img)
      Constructor for creating a "Titled" user with the specified attributes. This constructor initializes an instance of the Usuario class with the provided values for user details, including the user's ID, name, birth date, email, password, avatar, study title, study place, title date, and title image. Additionally, the user's role is set to "TITLED".
      Parameters:
      id - String which collects the ObjectId of the user.
      name - String with the user's name.
      fechaNac - LocalDate with the user's birthday.
      email - String with the user's email address.
      password - String with the user's password.
      avatar - String with the avatar image URL of the user.
      studies_title - String with the title of the user's studies.
      study_place - String with the institution where the user completed her/his studies.
      title_date - LocalDate with the date when the user obtained their title.
      title_img - the image associated with the user's title.
